{"tid":1218011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 有人買物資比人偷哂啲 而家無哂錢 點好？","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T11:57:24.000Z","uid":151909,"like":155,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"500c47254d7f94076c7656aeff913cbd0b3914b4","tid":1218011,"uid":151909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"Sorry呃大家入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEVgCN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEVgCN3.png&h=5d9a9186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但如果喺呢個時候<br />\n仲有人喺到做埋啲 同呃死人錢無分別既事<br />\n真係睇唔過睇<br />\n對鞋炒價7000幾<br />\n係咪想再賺多啲<br />\n就打埋句買物資用哂錢？<br />\n如果係既話 真係無野好講<br />\n大佬 打緊仗 可唔可以唔好做埋啲陰側野？<br />\n既然佢咁等錢洗 不如大家幫下佢<br />\n我諗如果唔等錢洗 都唔會做到咁<br />\n大家幫下佢 第一個利用呢件事搵錢既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b275d3cdb4df005d65b9c424a3665faa64c5df","tid":1218011,"uid":149773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢位義士出錢出力 大家要幫下佢散貨啦 唔知名點幫佢手"},{"pid":"623d3544c066eaf46c83d4975ba8849ccb024b4b","tid":1218011,"uid":151909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錢點好？"},{"pid":"ffc2f20b67775e2ac93493d4255cb6966a689609","tid":1218011,"uid":203702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da22c9af3b57281ba680f30419982171cd667c8b","tid":1218011,"uid":247138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:50:19.000Z"